additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children. Irritant. Causes serious eye irritation. Causes skin irritation. Avoid contact with eyes and skin. Do not ingest. Contains Subtilisin. May produce an allergic reaction. Close the bag properly. For advice, contact a Poisons Information Centre (Phone Australia: 1311 26; New Zealand 0800 764 766) or a doctor in case of contact with eyes or skin, rinse immediately with plenty of water. If irritation persists, seek medical advice. If a child puts tablet into the mouth, remove immediately. If contents have been released, rinse the mouth out thoroughly.
